    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/6b39ce9ab9c470f8ac2c830837c843ef.poster.avif?t=1762790287\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/6b39ce9ab9c470f8ac2c830837c843ef.webm?t=1762790287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/6b39ce9ab9c470f8ac2c830837c843ef.mp4?t=1762790287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维塔·卢西斯是一名来自私人教会公会的雇佣兵，拥有恶魔之力。组建一支教会恶魔小队，踏上黑暗奇幻动作冒险之旅。对上帝的信仰在某种程度上是个错误——诅咒、恶魔和其他邪灵确实存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/1f32c657db794b21630e860a7f354271.poster.avif?t=1762790287\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/1f32c657db794b21630e860a7f354271.webm?t=1762790287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/1f32c657db794b21630e860a7f354271.mp4?t=1762790287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态战斗系统，角色切换可在关键时刻使用独特技能。战斗中，你将操控一名英雄，而你的小队成员则独立行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/2c11a6a3b39e00804d11777b672c8626.avif?t=1762790287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras_big/2c11a6a3b39e00804d11777b672c8626.avif?t=1762790287 width=1560 height=520 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建一支由各具特色的雇佣兵组成的队伍，每个雇佣兵都有自己的故事、动机和技能。尝试不同的队伍组合，选择你喜欢的游戏风格来对抗邪恶势力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/0904d42f00d4cb74fc05b3a07bbd6d30.avif?t=1762790287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras_big/0904d42f00d4cb74fc05b3a07bbd6d30.avif?t=1762790287 width=1560 height=520 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个濒临毁灭的残酷世界。看似平静的定居点暗藏阴谋和匪患，公路上也充斥着怪物和强盗。重返之前探索过的地点，发现新的兴趣点，解锁额外任务，并影响主线剧情的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras/a76a7204172f8964a177bef1954e1f88.avif?t=1762790287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187120/extras_big/a76a7204172f8964a177bef1954e1f88.avif?t=1762790287 width=1560 height=520 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >维塔违背自己的意愿获得了对抗邪恶的力量。她是唯一知道自己名字的人，因为她开始记起自己的过去，包括与被囚禁在武器中的恶魔缔结契约的过程。揭开世界的黑暗秘密，解开遗忘预言。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 俄语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 阿拉伯语, 简体中文, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 土耳其语, 捷克语, 日语, 塞尔维亚语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
